        <title>Ruby Psych库中的ReDoS漏洞分析与修复</title>
        <link>http://localhost:1313/p/ruby-psych%E5%BA%93%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84redos%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E4%B8%8E%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D/</link>
